title: Mighty Blaster Hose Nozzle Is the Only Nozzle You'll Ever Need
description: From a delicate mist to a forceful power wash, this lightweight, easy-to-adjust hose nozzle is perfect for all of your outdoor needs. With 50% more force than traditional nozzles, the pressure control technology will change the way you work outdoors and meet all of your watering and power washing needs.

transcripts: Leaky plastic Sprayers shoot water everywhere except where you want it. And power washers are bulky, heavy, and a pain to set up. Introducing the Mighty Blaster fireman's nozzle. The first ever household sprayer with the power and precision of a real fireman's nozzle. Mighty Blaster has 50% more power so you can effortlessly reach your roof and quickly clean all your dirty eaves with ease. Or blast away dirt, leaves, and twigs from sidewalks and driveways. Even these large stones. Try to do that with another. Developed using the same power pressure technology in professional fire nozzles, Mighty Blaster packs a punch easily plowing through this line of stones, even taking down this giant one. And it's built to last. Featuring aircraft grade aluminum and quality stainless steel. But best of all, the comfort grip allows you to use it much longer than those traditional sprayers and without hurting your hands. Plus the convenient control knob turns it on and off Instantly. Adjusting mighty blaster is simple. The infinite control goes from a fine mist all the way to the most powerful blast. So gently water the most delicate flowers. then just give it a twist to bring on the power. Scour mold and mildew of the outside of your home in seconds. Easily blast away even the hardest caked on mud for a shine like new or wash a year's worth of dirt and grime off patio furniture or from around the pool. The power this has is amazing. You can really feel it as soon as you turn on the water that makes every job so much easier. I love it!
